# 🏗️ TOSS Platform Architecture v2

## 🎯 Purpose
The TOSS Platform is a **modular, extensible ERP III system** designed to empower township and rural-based enterprises through:
- Core ERP capabilities
- AI-powered Copilot for guided workflows
- Peer-to-peer cooperative supply chain coordination
- Domain-first modeling with Clean Architecture

---

## 🧱 Layered Architecture (Clean DDD)

```plaintext
+-----------------------+
|      Presentation     |   → Nuxt.js (Admin & Web), Flutter (Mobile POS)
+-----------------------+
           │
           ▼
+-----------------------+
|    Application Layer  |   → CQRS, MediatR, UseCases, Orchestrators
+-----------------------+
           │
           ▼
+-----------------------+
|      Domain Layer      |   → Aggregates, Entities, ValueObjects, DomainEvents
+-----------------------+
           │
           ▼
+-----------------------+
|   Infrastructure Layer |  → EF Core, PostgreSQL, Redis, RabbitMQ, Blob Storage
+-----------------------+
           │
           ▼
+-----------------------+
|     External Services  |  → Copilot AI (Semantic Kernel), Payment APIs, SMS, OAuth
+-----------------------+
